Designed specifically for the angler who is serious about crankbait fishing, Lew’s is excited to announce the release of the 2022 XD Cranking Series. 

“You can feel the perfect harmony of backbone and load in this rod when you are making those long crankbait casts, even with a lighter lure,” - @markdavisbasspro, 35-year pro angling veteran and bonafide crankbait expert. “It’s just so well balanced, with the forgiving blend of glass and the strength of some of the best graphite out there.”

Hear more about the XD Cranking Series & all new products from @icastshow at the link in our bio.

Who's ready for a new episode of KINGS OF BASS?! Air date is 𝐌𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐉𝐮𝐧𝐞 𝟐𝟖 𝐚𝐭 𝟕𝐩𝐦 𝐄𝐓 𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐞𝐰'𝐬 𝐈𝐆𝐓𝐕 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐓𝐮𝐛𝐞.

Reunited on the water for the first time in years. @mark_zona_fishing phones a friend and puts on a beatdown of epic proportions with @kevinvandamfishing on Lake St. Clair! Go behind the scenes and see how Z prepares to film a fishing show and hear how bass fishing has changed his life.

@greghackneyfishing continues his quest to qualify for the #BassmasterClassic at Lake Fork. Follow his journey as he tackles one of the greatest bass fishing lakes and learn how he got into the sport we all love.

node.text:
Congratulations to @johnny_byrd_gone_fishing on winning our first Kings of Bass TV giveaway! 👏 

The South Carolina native traveled to Lew's HQ to pick up his prizes and share some of what fishing means to him. As a member of Fishers of Men, he has the opportunity to fish in tournaments at Lake Santee and Lake Murray yearround. 

In a recent tournament while fishing with his wife, John's Lew's Pro TI rod snapped while boating a hawg! What a perfect time to set him up with a brand new Andy Montgomery Signature series rod, a Pro SP, and a handful of @strikekinglurecompany baits. Thank you John for being such a loyal customer, and good luck in your upcoming tournaments!

[[NEW GIVEAWAY ANNOUNCEMENT 8/29 AT 8PM EST]]

#TeamLews #Lews #LewsFishing #SignatureSeries #StrikeKing #giveawaywinner #KingsofBass #KingsOfBassTV

[NEW VIDEO 🎥 LINK IN BIO] Lew's and Strike King are proud to partner with Casting Freedom - a program that aims to send combat wounded veterans, veterans, and Gold Star Family members enough fishing equipment to get out on the water and enjoy the therapeutic benefits of the outdoors.

---

Major League Fishing angler and U.S. Army veteran Jeff Sprague is joined on the water by Sergeant Jake Ziliani of the United States Marine Corps.

Hear from Cpl. Ron Potter - Founder of Casting Freedom - on how the outdoors provided him an outlet to cope with combat traumas leading to the creation of Casting Freedom.

Andy Montgomery and Lance Corporal Patrick Gibson - United States Marine Corps - go toe to toe hooking largemouth bass while sharing a laugh or two.

#Lews #TeamLews #AmericanHero #veteran #castingfreedom #StrikeKing #USArmy #USMarineCorps #fishing #bassfishing #outdoors #outdoortherapy
